content: गुणनं [गुण्-ल्युट्] {@--1@} Multiplication. {@--2@} Enumeration. {@--3@} Describing merits or qualities, pointing out or enumerating merits; इह रसभणने कृतहरिगुणने मधुरिपुपदसेवके <ls>Gīt. 7.</ls> --नी Examining books, studying; collating and correcting copies to determine the value of variants.
